            "content": "## Description\n\nImplements org-level automation sharing, allowing team members to view and fork each other's automation configurations. Key changes:\n\n**Data model & backend:**\n- Firestore `organizations/{orgId}/automations/{automationId}` stores shared automation metadata\n- UUID stored in HEARTBEAT.md frontmatter (`id` field), generated on first sync via `crypto.randomUUID()`\n- 5 backend API routes: sync, list, get, fork, visual upload (S3)\n- S3 storage for VISUAL.html at `automations/{orgId}/{automationId}/sessions/{sessionId}/visual.html`\n\n**Daemon:**\n- `syncAutomationsToBackend()` pushes local automations to Firestore on startup\n- `uploadVisualToBackend()` uploads session visual HTML to S3\n- Privacy controls: `handleUpdateAutomationPrivacy()` updates HEARTBEAT.md frontmatter\n- Clean RPC param naming: `automationDirName` (directory slug) vs `automationId` (UUID in results)\n- `getAutomationDirName()` helper for consistent extraction across all 8 automation handlers\n\n**Frontend:**\n- Dual-source merge: local automations (daemon RPC) + shared automations (backend API)\n- Ownership filter dropdown (All / Private / Shared)\n- \"Shared\" label with globe icon on shared automation cards\n- Disabled controls with tooltips for non-owned automations\n- Share modal for toggling privacy level\n- Fork button to create local copy of shared automation\n- Session source tagging with `platform=automation` and `automationId` (UUID)\n\n**UI polish:**\n- Avatar size reduced to 14px with transform scale\n- Split \"Visibility\" and \"Owner\" sections in detail panel\n- Pencil icon for inline share modal trigger\n\n### Screenshots\n\n**Automations grid with \"Shared\" label and ownership filter:**\n\n![Automations Grid](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/placeholder-grid)\n<!-- See /tmp/e2e-automations-grid.png -->\n\n**Ownership filter dropdown (All / Private / Shared):**\n\n![Ownership Filter](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/